Initial release 1.0.0

This plugin allows to watch the videos from the TV5MONDE web site, selected by category and ordered by date.

This is the first release of the plugin.

To install it simply download the zip file, and then proceed as with any other plugin from XBMC:
 System->Settings->Add-ons->Install from zip file.

Any issues detected can be reported using this forum thread for support: http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid=152992

Enjoy it!
